name: Pump it!
description: This NFT is my genesis piece minted on hicetnunc.xyz and it's forever connected with physical oil painting dimm.100x80 cm, made in Warsaw, Poland by me - Dominik Jalowinski in march 2021, when Bitcoin was at ath. If You buy it I'm going to deliver this painting to You at my cost and so should do every new owner in case of further sales. This NFT as well as painting and lenticular print was presented at exhibition "Void Connoisseur" in WIDNA Gallery IG @ during Cracow Art Week https://cracowartweek.pl/void-connoisseur/ on june 2021. There is also a virtual version of exhibition on https://www.cryptovoxels.com/s/widna You can see my other works on IG @dj_alowinski
